**Example 1: 修改别称域名**



Input: 

```
tccli teo ModifyAliasDomain --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --TargetName bbb.example.com \
    --AliasName eo.test.com \
    --CertType none \
    --ZoneId zone-28569s6od5na
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "RequestId": "6d1efe51-b951-498e-9b10-755906835e87"
    }
}
```
